@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vnhdoi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v0 + ((tmp + 0.58 + v2 + 0.16) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.40)))
    v0 = wp.cos((0.42 * 0.86))
    v1 = (0.80 + v1)
    v0 = wp.abs((0.59 - (v1 + 0.14 / v0 + 0.16)))
    v0 = 0.83
    data[tid] = v0
